name: POWERSKULL_04 - Iridium Teleportation Cranium
description:
Master Alchemists of an ancient tribe from the extinct planet 396-Gamma were responsible for crafting the POWERSKULLZ.

The Legends from the Great Elders describe how this Iridium Teleportation Cranium gave the ability to spatially dislocate in an instantaneous fashion to whoever grasped it with both hands and elevated it to eye level.

This artefact would only work when handled by a human being. The skull's resonant frequency is in tune with the electromagnetic field emanated by humans. The POWERSKULL would disintegrate the physical and ethereal bodies of the skull-bearer, to instantly reintegrate them wherever the human so desires.

Other living forms' magnetic fields would not be tuned to the Iridium Teleportation Cranium and would not activate it.

The POWERSKULLZ are part of the POWERVERSE, a reality where humans have achieved their highest potential and live as gods.
